-- Cineplex Odeon, Pyramid Saimara May Bid For Hoyts Cinemas, Australian Says
-- B y   E l i s a b e t h   B e h r m a n n
-- 2010-12-08T20:55:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/cineplex-odeon-pyramid-saimara-may-bid-for-hoyts-cinemas-australian-says.html
 Cineplex Odeon Corp., India’s
Pyramid Saimira Theatre Ltd. and private equity firm Archer
Capital are among potential bidders for Pacific Equity Partners’
Hoyts Cinemas Group, the Australian newspaper reported, without
saying where it got the information. Preparations for the sale,
which may fetch more than A$500 million, are part of a dual-
track process that includes a potential initial share sale, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisabeth Behrmann in Sydney at 
